<h2>
    <strong>Oregon Fishing License and Regulations Overview</strong>
</h2>
<p>
    To fish legally in Hillsboro:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Angling license</strong> required for ages 12+.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Trout harvest tag</strong> usually not needed in stocked ponds.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Combined Angling Tag</strong> required for salmon/steelhead.
