    <strong>Q1: Where can I fish without a boat in Hillsboro?</strong><br>
    Rood Bridge Park, Bethany Lake, and Commonwealth Lake all offer great bank fishing.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Q2: What fish are in the Tualatin River?</strong><br>
